<br>
DN is not too bad, I think location (out of the way) hurts it more than content, some anoying phase shifts from the spiders but nothing too bad. <br>
<br>
Velks, perhaps they are trying to make it so ppl ocupy more of it again? I dunno it seems fine compared to many others.<br>
<br>
